	('"I got it" she yelled','"Tớ lấy được rồi này" Cô bé hét lên','00:01:53.800','00:01:55.800','4000-essential-english-words-23'),
	('The blue team won','Đội xanh đã thắng rồi','00:01:55.800','00:01:57.600','4000-essential-english-words-23'),
