	/* ('4000 Essential English Words - Volume 5: Lesson 14 - Day Without Sight','4000 Từ Tiếng Anh Quan Trọng - Tập 5: Bài 14 - Ngày không có thị giác','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'), */
	('On Friday afternoon, Sam\'s teacher had a special assignment','Vào chiều thứ Sáu, giáo viên của Sam đã đưa ra 1 nhiệm vụ đặc biệt','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('"Next week, we\'ll be studying humanitarian efforts around the world since the time of the Renaissance, including those to help the blind," she said','"Tuần tới, chúng ta sẽ nghiên cứu về những nỗ lực nhân đạo trên toàn thế giới từ thời kỳ Phục hưng bao gồm việc giúp đỡ người mù," cô ấy nói','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('"Over the weekend, I want each of you to wear a blindfold for an entire day"','"Trong cuối tuần này, cô muốn mỗi người trong các bạn đeo bịt mắt trong cả ngày"','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('"The premise of this experiment is that it will help you understand what it\'s like to be blind," she said','"Tiền đề của trải nghiệm này sẽ giúp các em hiểu việc không nhìn thấy gì sẽ như thế nào," cô ấy nói','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('Sam was a skeptic','Sam là một người đa nghi','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He really didn\'t think the assignment would be too challenging','Cậu đã không thực sự nghĩ rằng nhiệm vụ này sẽ quá thách thức','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('On Saturday morning, Sam took a piece of cloth and tied it around his head to cover his eyes','Vào sáng thứ Bảy, Sam lấy một miếng vải và buộc nó vòng quanh đầu để che mắt','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('Then he went into the kitchen for breakfast','Sau đó cậu ấy đi vào nhà bếp để ăn sáng','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He heard the voices of his parents and brothers but couldn\'t specify where each voice was coming from','Cậu ấy nghe thấy tiếng nói của ba mẹ và các anh em nhưng không thể xác định nơi chúng phát ra','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He thought about how important hearing is for blind people','Cậu ấy nghĩ việc nghe thật quan trọng đối với người mù','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('"Could you pass me the newspaper, please?" he asked','"Em có thể đưa cho anh tờ báo được không?" cậu ấy hỏi','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('Just then, he remembered he couldn\'t see the words on the page','Ngay sau đó, cậu ấy nhớ ra mình không thể nhìn thấy các dòng chữ trên tờ báo','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He wondered if Braille newspapers were ever made','Cậu ấy tự hỏi liệu rằng báo chữ nổi đã được làm ra chưa','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('After finishing breakfast, his brothers asked him to play soccer','Sau bữa sáng, các anh em trai rủ cậu cùng chơi bóng đá','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('As he followed them, he accidentally walked into the baker\'s rack','Khi đi theo họ, cậu ấy đã vô tình va vào kệ tủ của người thợ làm bánh','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He also found that he couldn\'t play soccer','Cậu ấy cũng nhận ra rằng mình không thể chơi bóng đá','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
