	('He sat on the lawn','Cậu ấy ngồi trên bãi cỏ','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('Suddenly, he realized that though he couldn\'t see, his other senses worked perfectly fine','Bất chợt, cậu nhận ra rằng vì mình không thể nhìn thấy, các giác quan khác hoạt động hoàn toàn ổn','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('In fact, he began to realize new and different aspects of common objects','Thực tế, cậu bắt đậu nhận ra khía cạnh mới và khác nhau của những vật thông thường','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('For example, he took a flower bud and felt it with his finger','Ví dụ, cậu bé nhặt lấy 1 nụ hoa và cảm nhận nó bằng ngón tay','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('He realized for the first time that it seemed to be covered with wax','Lần đầu tiên cậu bé nhận thấy rằng nó có vẻ như được bao phủ bằng lông','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
	('His hypothesis about being blind was disproved','Giả thuyết của cậu bé về việc bị mù đã bị bác bỏ','','','4000-essential-english-words-134'),
